WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 15=

01:43.380 --> 01:44.850
Mr. Song, you're here

01:44.850 --> 01:46.570
for the Jade Sunflower, right?

01:47.380 --> 01:49.050
Once I take the Bliss Palace

01:49.050 --> 01:50.620
and find the Jade Sunflower,

01:50.620 --> 01:51.930
I'll have someone send it to you.

01:52.380 --> 01:53.740
As for other matters,

01:54.180 --> 01:55.330
you need not trouble yourself.

01:55.820 --> 01:57.130
Zhao's Gu poison isn't cured yet,

01:57.820 --> 01:58.980
so I should stay here.

01:59.330 --> 02:00.900
I also want to help Mr. Mu

02:01.490 --> 02:03.050
eliminate Nie Zhe soon.

02:04.740 --> 02:07.770
To find the Jade Sunflower sooner

02:07.770 --> 02:08.690
and regain your powers,

02:09.060 --> 02:11.780
you'd even collude with
a demon sect member like me?

02:12.170 --> 02:13.260
Collude?

02:13.890 --> 02:15.290
Mr. Mu, what are you talking about?

02:15.290 --> 02:17.060
Yuzhi only meant well.

02:17.060 --> 02:18.820
I was speaking with Mr. Song,

02:18.820 --> 02:20.290
why did Zhao follow us in?

02:20.290 --> 02:21.690
I brought Yuzhi here.

02:21.690 --> 02:23.010
Naturally, I must ensure his safety.

02:24.260 --> 02:25.730
Mr. Mu, there's no need to worry.

02:26.100 --> 02:27.540
On this trip to the Li Sect,

02:27.540 --> 02:29.100
I should have protected Zhao.

02:29.500 --> 02:31.060
Yet I let her suffer this calamity.

02:31.500 --> 02:33.780
I'll stop at nothing to find an antidote

02:33.780 --> 02:35.660
and kill the ringleader Nie Zhe.

02:35.660 --> 02:36.890
That is the first reason.

02:36.890 --> 02:38.380
Nie Zhe slaughtered the innocent,

02:38.380 --> 02:39.540
refined corpse slaves and

02:39.540 --> 02:40.380
went against all reason.

02:40.390 --> 02:41.410
The world resents him.

02:41.410 --> 02:43.730
How can the Six Sects of Beichen
stand by?

02:43.730 --> 02:45.130
That is the second reason.

02:45.130 --> 02:46.290
Once I return to the Qingque Sect,

02:46.290 --> 02:48.540
I will report the situation here
to my elders.

02:48.540 --> 02:49.660
I'm sure Master

02:49.660 --> 02:51.820
and the other elders
will approve of my actions.

02:53.780 --> 02:54.620
Yuzhi.

02:55.100 --> 02:55.940
You...

02:56.660 --> 02:57.500
You're right.

02:58.060 --> 02:59.010
But,

02:59.010 --> 03:00.500
when it comes to
reporting to our elders,

03:00.500 --> 03:01.340
we'd better

03:01.340 --> 03:02.660
think it over once more.

03:03.100 --> 03:04.010
To put it plainly,

03:04.850 --> 03:06.820
it's all for the Jade Sunflower.

03:10.100 --> 03:10.940
Mr. Mu,

03:11.340 --> 03:13.260
did you brew some medicine for me?

03:13.890 --> 03:15.220
It should be nearly ready, right?

03:23.010 --> 03:23.890
Oh, right,

03:23.890 --> 03:25.010
the herbal garden should be

03:25.010 --> 03:27.380
in the valley five miles to
the left of the Youming Path.

03:28.570 --> 03:29.610
You've worked hard.

03:29.610 --> 03:30.450
Okay.

03:46.690 --> 03:47.980
Why did you pull me out here?

03:49.060 --> 03:50.690
Scared I'd drive Song Yuzhi crazy?

03:51.130 --> 03:53.260
Scared he'd drive you crazy.

03:53.780 --> 03:56.130
Yuzhi is focused and righteous.

03:56.130 --> 03:58.010
No question you ask can stump him.

03:58.010 --> 03:59.540
You'll just end up fuming for nothing.

03:59.540 --> 04:00.380
Why bother?

04:03.540 --> 04:05.410
How focused

04:05.980 --> 04:07.500
and righteous.

04:08.290 --> 04:09.820
Once Miss Cai

04:09.820 --> 04:11.660
shakes off the corpse slave's Gu poison,

04:11.660 --> 04:13.500
leave here soon with

04:13.500 --> 04:14.980
your like-minded senior brother.

04:15.890 --> 04:17.700
After I seize the Bliss Palace treasury,

04:18.540 --> 04:19.380
I'll deliver

04:19.400 --> 04:21.290
the Jade Sunflower to you first.

04:21.730 --> 04:22.900
This place is filthy.

04:23.850 --> 04:25.140
I won't keep you here.

04:39.170 --> 04:40.050
No need for your cure.

04:40.730 --> 04:41.570
I'll leave on my own.

04:50.100 --> 04:50.940
You're not leaving.

04:53.410 --> 04:54.290
Let me go!

04:54.290 --> 04:55.410
I'll say this one last time.

04:55.810 --> 04:56.930
You're not leaving.

05:01.610 --> 05:02.450
Let go of me!

05:02.560 --> 05:03.410
I won't.

05:03.410 --> 05:04.250
Mr....

05:13.100 --> 05:13.940
What is it?

05:14.640 --> 05:16.710
Xing has prepared a herbal bath
for Miss Feng.

05:16.950 --> 05:18.140
Miss Feng, please come over.

05:22.900 --> 05:23.740
Please.

05:31.730 --> 05:33.610
If it weren't for you
saving me this time,

05:34.810 --> 05:36.540
I'd have died at Mu Qingyan

05:37.490 --> 05:38.850
and that sorceress's hands.

05:38.850 --> 05:41.700
Never thought she'd be
Cai Pingshu's niece.

05:41.700 --> 05:44.170
I hate that I didn't kill her then.

05:44.170 --> 05:46.980
To avenge Master and the brothers

05:46.980 --> 05:48.850
who died by Cai Pingshu's sword.

05:51.700 --> 05:53.140
Next time we meet,

05:54.340 --> 05:55.580
I won't spare her.

05:56.410 --> 05:57.410
No need to rush.

05:58.730 --> 05:59.930
Her identity

06:01.900 --> 06:04.220
might still be useful to us.

06:07.250 --> 06:08.930
Young Master specifically instructed us.

06:08.930 --> 06:10.250
He said Miss Feng

06:10.250 --> 06:12.490
is very particular about
food, clothing, and lodging.

06:12.490 --> 06:14.140
Every decoration in the room

06:14.140 --> 06:16.170
was arranged by Young Master himself.

06:16.170 --> 06:18.610
Young Master is so kind to you,
Miss Feng.

06:18.610 --> 06:19.540
It's okay.

06:20.140 --> 06:22.020
When he was recovering at Qingzhu Gang,

06:22.020 --> 06:23.290
I treated him well too.

06:23.980 --> 06:25.250
Exactly.

06:25.250 --> 06:27.170
Young Master's feelings for you

06:27.170 --> 06:28.050
are undeniable.

06:28.370 --> 06:29.490
What brings you here?

06:29.490 --> 06:30.330
Put it down.

06:38.220 --> 06:39.100
These

06:39.100 --> 06:41.220
are fresh flowers
the Young Master prepared for Miss Feng.

06:41.700 --> 06:43.850
The Young Master is truly thoughtful.

06:43.850 --> 06:44.810
Also,

06:44.810 --> 06:46.290
Mr. Dai has sent word.

06:46.290 --> 06:47.930
He said the herb garden
is still being searched.

06:47.930 --> 06:49.410
Please be patient, Miss Feng.

06:49.410 --> 06:51.610
Qingyun has been searching all night.

06:51.610 --> 06:52.900
Tell him to come back soon.

06:52.900 --> 06:56.020
Mr. Dai values you too, Miss Feng.

06:57.610 --> 06:59.490
That little bit of regard

06:59.490 --> 07:00.930
is nothing

07:00.930 --> 07:02.610
compared to Young Master
and Miss Feng's feelings.

07:02.610 --> 07:04.140
How can you tell?

07:04.140 --> 07:06.290
It's obvious to anyone with eyes.

07:06.290 --> 07:08.410
Though Miss Feng
is skilled in martial arts,

07:08.410 --> 07:11.250
she's still an inexperienced young lady.

07:11.250 --> 07:13.340
Young and lacking experience.

07:13.340 --> 07:15.370
Just worried about
Young Master's safety.

07:15.370 --> 07:17.410
Yet she traveled thousands of li

07:17.410 --> 07:19.140
to this dangerous Hanhai Mountains.

07:19.140 --> 07:21.700
Even as an outsider,

07:21.700 --> 07:22.780
my heart warms hearing that.

07:22.780 --> 07:24.700
If this isn't deep affection,

07:24.700 --> 07:26.410
what is?

07:27.340 --> 07:28.700
I agree.

07:28.700 --> 07:30.730
Miss Feng's loyalty
to Young Master

07:30.730 --> 07:32.250
is truly rare.

07:32.250 --> 07:34.050
This isn't just ordinary affection.

07:34.050 --> 07:35.610
- It's clearly...
- Oh, right.

07:35.610 --> 07:36.930
What was your name again?

07:36.930 --> 07:38.170
My surname is You.

07:38.170 --> 07:39.610
Given name, Guanyue.

07:40.050 --> 07:41.490
Guanyue.

07:42.020 --> 07:42.860
Then, Master You,

07:43.170 --> 07:44.580
do you often read storybooks?

07:45.170 --> 07:46.020
Not really.

07:46.220 --> 07:47.730
In storybooks, there's that kind of man.

07:47.730 --> 07:48.900
For the woman he likes

07:48.900 --> 07:50.100
but can't confess to,

07:50.580 --> 07:52.290
he secretly

07:52.290 --> 07:53.930
plays with her name.

07:53.930 --> 07:54.800
For instance,

07:54.800 --> 07:57.930
if that man's name has words
like "Shan" or "Feng,"

07:57.930 --> 07:59.170
he'll fondly call the lady,

07:59.170 --> 08:00.730
"Hua" or "Shui."

08:01.140 --> 08:01.980
Or

08:02.540 --> 08:04.780
"Xing" and "Yue."

08:07.100 --> 08:07.940
Interesting.

08:08.290 --> 08:09.370
Truly interesting.

08:09.810 --> 08:11.250
Why are we suddenly

08:11.730 --> 08:13.370
talking about storybooks?

08:14.100 --> 08:14.940
It's nothing.

08:15.140 --> 08:17.170
Miss Feng and I were just chatting idly.

08:21.810 --> 08:22.650
Mr. Mu.

08:23.760 --> 08:24.610
What is it?

08:24.610 --> 08:26.050
Rumors are spreading everywhere now.

08:26.050 --> 08:28.660
They say you're colluding with
our sect's sworn enemy.

08:28.660 --> 08:29.850
The descendants of Cai Pingshu.

08:29.850 --> 08:31.050
And plan to overturn the Li Sect.

08:35.650 --> 08:36.610
What?

08:36.610 --> 08:38.100
Dad went to the Hanhai Mountains?

08:38.100 --> 08:39.300
When Master left the mountain,

08:39.300 --> 08:41.130
he only told me to
handle sect affairs properly.

08:41.130 --> 08:42.610
Didn't say where he was going.

08:42.610 --> 08:44.250
But today a spy reported to Uncle Li.

08:44.250 --> 08:45.220
He said Master and Lord Song

08:45.220 --> 08:46.940
were spotted near the Hanhai Mountains.

08:46.940 --> 08:48.580
I suspect

08:48.580 --> 08:50.250
the demon sect is having major upheaval.

08:50.250 --> 08:51.610
So Master went in person,

08:51.610 --> 08:52.850
without disciples or men.

08:55.700 --> 08:56.540
Where are you going?

08:59.890 --> 09:00.770
To find Father.

09:00.770 --> 09:01.770
To seek Yuzhi.

09:01.770 --> 09:03.060
Yuzhi went to the demon sect too?

09:03.060 --> 09:04.060
When?

09:04.060 --> 09:05.180
Cai Zhao went as well.

09:05.180 --> 09:06.420
They left the mountain together.

09:06.980 --> 09:08.060
Stop!

09:10.490 --> 09:11.420
Mother.

09:11.420 --> 09:12.890
Stay quietly within the sect.

09:15.250 --> 09:16.730
What can you do if you rush over now?

09:17.060 --> 09:17.900
I…

09:18.250 --> 09:19.300
I can help Father.

09:19.300 --> 09:20.650
Why did your father go alone?

09:20.650 --> 09:21.890
He wished to keep this matter quiet.

09:21.890 --> 09:22.980
You rushed over in such a hurry.

09:22.980 --> 09:25.180
Do you want
the whole sect to know about it?

09:25.180 --> 09:26.340
If Yuzhi is safe, great.

09:26.340 --> 09:27.180
If not,

09:27.180 --> 09:28.300
how will you fix it?

09:28.980 --> 09:29.820
I...

09:31.340 --> 09:33.010
I know you can't let go.

09:33.010 --> 09:34.770
But if you still want to marry Yuzhi,

09:34.770 --> 09:36.530
you must learn to
prioritize the bigger picture.

09:36.530 --> 09:37.650
Don't be

09:37.650 --> 09:38.890
too rigid about some things.

09:39.370 --> 09:40.220
Pretend

09:40.770 --> 09:42.130
you don't know some things.

09:42.650 --> 09:43.490
Mother,

09:43.490 --> 09:45.300
I'm not as skilled as Cai Zhao,

09:45.300 --> 09:47.220
but I'm not useless either.

09:47.220 --> 09:49.180
With your Father and Uncle there,

09:49.180 --> 09:51.300
they'll surely keep Yuzhi safe.

09:51.300 --> 09:52.180
Besides,

09:52.180 --> 09:54.370
that Cai girl is very proud.

09:54.370 --> 09:55.980
She won't do anything shameful

09:55.980 --> 09:57.580
to dishonor Luoying Valley.

09:59.890 --> 10:02.220
Miss Feng is Cai Pingshu's niece.

10:02.220 --> 10:03.370
Is that for real?

10:03.520 --> 10:04.740
Last time at the Xuanwu Altar,

10:04.850 --> 10:06.730
I had doubts
when I saw the Sunshine Blade.

10:06.730 --> 10:07.570
Never thought

10:08.180 --> 10:09.030
she truly was the heir

10:09.030 --> 10:10.300
of that devil Cai Pingshu.

10:10.300 --> 10:12.180
Back then,
the former Chief refined corpse slaves,

10:13.060 --> 10:14.530
and captured many Six Sects disciples.

10:15.130 --> 10:17.180
Cai Pingshu stormed
the Youming Path three times

10:17.550 --> 10:18.850
and killed countless sect members.

10:19.250 --> 10:20.250
If this news leaks,

10:20.580 --> 10:21.980
the Young Master
will be in a terrible spot.

10:23.700 --> 10:25.100
Then we have to cover it up!

10:25.100 --> 10:27.420
The entire Li Sect
submits to Young Master now.

10:27.420 --> 10:29.490
If Cai Pingshu's heir pops up,

10:29.490 --> 10:30.730
what then?

10:30.730 --> 10:31.940
Attack the Bliss Palace or not?

10:31.940 --> 10:33.340
Go for the Chief position or not?

10:33.340 --> 10:34.220
The only way now is

10:34.220 --> 10:35.820
to persuade Young Master to cut ties

10:35.820 --> 10:36.850
with Miss Cai immediately.

10:38.300 --> 10:39.980
Cai Pingshu is Cai Pingshu.

10:39.980 --> 10:41.700
Miss Cai is Miss Cai.

10:41.700 --> 10:42.770
What's wrong with

10:42.770 --> 10:44.220
the Young Master liking a girl?

10:46.130 --> 10:46.970
Xing,

10:47.300 --> 10:49.340
it's not about liking or not.

10:49.340 --> 10:51.220
Cai Pingshu killed
so many elders of the Li Sect,

10:52.670 --> 10:54.010
including Elder Shangguan's uncle,

10:54.010 --> 10:55.100
Elder Yaoguang,

10:55.700 --> 10:56.650
and even my adoptive father,

10:57.130 --> 10:58.100
Elder Qiu.

10:58.700 --> 11:00.580
All nearly perished
at Cai Pingshu's hands.

11:00.940 --> 11:02.250
How could such a blood feud

11:02.980 --> 11:04.250
be settled?

11:05.730 --> 11:08.420
But Young Master always has a cold face.

11:08.420 --> 11:10.530
Only when he sees Miss Cai

11:11.060 --> 11:13.250
does he crack a small smile.

11:14.890 --> 11:15.730
Can't

11:16.340 --> 11:18.180
we just deny the rumors outright?

11:18.180 --> 11:20.650
Pretend Miss Cai is still Miss Feng.

11:20.980 --> 11:21.980
These rumors

11:22.650 --> 11:24.530
were likely spread on purpose
by someone.

11:24.530 --> 11:25.940
Young Master can't just deny them.

11:25.940 --> 11:27.490
Back then, the Young Master's father

11:27.490 --> 11:28.850
let his emotions rule him,

11:29.650 --> 11:31.060
so he lived a miserable half-life

11:31.650 --> 11:32.980
and died young.

11:35.940 --> 11:36.860
(Qinglong Altar)

11:36.890 --> 11:38.700
Why hasn't Yuzhi returned yet?

11:40.650 --> 11:41.490
Miss Feng.

11:43.420 --> 11:44.260
Xing.

11:46.650 --> 11:47.890
Miss Cai.

11:49.770 --> 11:50.610
I heard...

11:50.670 --> 11:52.220
the village chief and the others
are leaving.

11:52.580 --> 11:54.250
Yes. Young Master is kind.

11:54.460 --> 11:55.890
Afraid Nie Zhe
will take revenge secretly.

11:56.490 --> 11:58.060
He wants them to come back

11:58.060 --> 11:59.700
when the sect is more stable.

11:59.700 --> 12:01.610
Look, Young Master specially

12:01.610 --> 12:03.010
told me to hand out these

12:03.010 --> 12:04.220
insect repellent sachets to everyone.

12:07.730 --> 12:08.570
Xing,

12:09.300 --> 12:10.850
help me pass a message to Uncle Xue,

12:11.180 --> 12:12.020
just tell him

12:12.340 --> 12:13.980
I need his help with something.

12:21.060 --> 12:22.580
Sunshine Blade?

12:23.530 --> 12:25.820
She really is Cai Pingshu's niece.

12:26.650 --> 12:27.650
If I'd known,

12:28.180 --> 12:29.850
I never would've saved you.

12:30.130 --> 12:31.060
Back in the day,

12:31.060 --> 12:32.730
the former Chief and countless members

12:33.180 --> 12:35.220
died horribly at Cai Pingshu's hands.

12:35.580 --> 12:36.420
Cai clan

12:37.180 --> 12:40.180
and our Li Sect are mortal enemies!

12:40.360 --> 12:41.220
She's her.

12:41.220 --> 12:42.530
Her aunt is her aunt.

12:42.820 --> 12:44.340
Elder Yan, don't you forget.

12:44.610 --> 12:45.820
Back at the Xuanwu Altar,

12:46.130 --> 12:48.130
Miss Cai saved Young Master

12:48.130 --> 12:49.370
and so many of our members.

12:49.370 --> 12:50.370
Nonsense.

12:50.740 --> 12:53.180
The Six Sects of Beichen
are always hypocritical and deceitful.

12:53.650 --> 12:55.820
Who knows if she's
bewitching Young Master?

12:55.820 --> 12:56.660
Today,

12:56.680 --> 12:58.420
I'll eliminate this traitor for Li Sect.

12:58.420 --> 13:01.420
I won't let our 200-year legacy

13:01.420 --> 13:02.980
be destroyed by a Cai clan woman!

13:02.980 --> 13:05.180
Zhao and I came here with no ill intent.

13:05.180 --> 13:06.820
But if you keep threatening us
with weapons,

13:06.820 --> 13:08.580
we won't surrender willingly.

13:08.580 --> 13:09.940
It's just a battle.

13:10.370 --> 13:11.210
Enough.

13:20.890 --> 13:21.730
Elder Yan,

13:22.130 --> 13:23.220
what do you mean by this?

13:23.730 --> 13:26.890
Mr. Mu keeps getting entangled with
this Cai witch.

13:26.890 --> 13:27.980
Are you

13:27.980 --> 13:30.770
abandoning the entire Li Sect?

13:30.770 --> 13:32.180
So the rumors are true.

13:32.180 --> 13:34.250
Young Master really is
in cahoots with the Six Sects' devils.

13:34.250 --> 13:36.300
This woman really is
that devil Cai Pingshu's heir.

13:36.770 --> 13:37.610
Elder Yan.

13:38.100 --> 13:40.530
It's clearly a setup to stir up trouble.

13:40.890 --> 13:42.770
We can't fall for it!

13:43.420 --> 13:45.490
Miss Cai has done our Li Sect
a great favor.

13:45.490 --> 13:46.340
Why not

13:46.770 --> 13:48.530
let bygones be bygones?

13:48.530 --> 13:50.010
Just let her
leave the Hanhai Mountains...

13:50.010 --> 13:52.220
A bunch of bitter, useless fools.

13:52.530 --> 13:53.940
Back in the Battle of Mount Tu,

13:54.300 --> 13:56.580
when Cai Pingshu fought Nie Hengcheng,

13:56.580 --> 13:57.770
did she use hidden weapons?

13:58.180 --> 13:59.530
Did she set a trap?

14:00.770 --> 14:02.180
Did she win by outnumbering his foe?

14:03.220 --> 14:05.180
It was a fair fight to the death.

14:06.010 --> 14:07.370
Victory or defeat was fate.

14:07.940 --> 14:09.530
Nie Hengcheng was a generation older

14:09.530 --> 14:11.180
and over ten years older

14:11.420 --> 14:13.180
than Cai Pingshu.

14:13.700 --> 14:15.370
Yet in the end, he was outmatched.

14:15.730 --> 14:16.980
He was killed and beheaded.

14:17.220 --> 14:19.420
Such disgrace brought upon us.

14:20.130 --> 14:21.610
And you still dare to speak of it.

14:22.490 --> 14:23.530
Do you feel no shame?

14:25.900 --> 14:27.420
The Li Sect has hidden
in the Hanhai Mountains

14:27.420 --> 14:28.490
for 200 years.

14:29.890 --> 14:31.700
It's time to step out into the world.

14:32.180 --> 14:33.820
Now the mountain gate is open.

14:34.180 --> 14:35.730
Stay or leave,

14:36.890 --> 14:38.180
it's your choice.

14:40.610 --> 14:42.010
As for Cai Pingshu's niece,

14:42.580 --> 14:43.940
she's my closest friend.

14:44.850 --> 14:46.980
If anyone here dares harm her,

14:47.940 --> 14:49.300
I'll kill them.

14:50.060 --> 14:51.180
Without the slightest mercy.

14:53.730 --> 14:55.250
For over a hundred years

14:55.250 --> 14:57.220
the Mu clan has always acted

14:57.220 --> 14:58.770
without thinking.

14:58.770 --> 15:00.300
Letting emotions rule.

15:00.300 --> 15:01.220
At best,

15:01.220 --> 15:02.940
it tears families apart.

15:02.940 --> 15:03.780
At worst,

15:04.490 --> 15:06.370
it brings bloodshed to the sect.

15:06.890 --> 15:07.770
Fine.

15:07.770 --> 15:10.180
I'll see how this ends for you.

15:10.770 --> 15:11.610
Go!

15:15.610 --> 15:16.450
Guanyue.

15:17.700 --> 15:18.730
If they wish to leave,

15:20.010 --> 15:20.850
let them go.

15:21.340 --> 15:22.180
Don't stop them.

15:23.420 --> 15:24.610
Also, find out

15:25.250 --> 15:28.010
who's spreading these rumors.

15:29.220 --> 15:30.650
Kill them without mercy.

15:31.580 --> 15:33.060
Yes, Mr. Mu.

15:40.730 --> 15:41.980
Have you found the herb garden?

15:48.530 --> 15:49.650
Everyone behind, keep up.

15:49.650 --> 15:51.060
Hurry, hurry and keep up.

15:51.060 --> 15:52.340
Keep up, let's go.

15:52.340 --> 15:53.180
Hurry up.

15:54.010 --> 15:54.850
Go.

15:55.490 --> 15:56.330
Brother.

15:58.220 --> 15:59.610
May I ask you something?

15:59.610 --> 16:00.450
What's happening

16:00.450 --> 16:01.730
at the Li Sect?

16:01.730 --> 16:03.420
Where's all this fire coming from?

16:03.420 --> 16:04.610
Mr. Mu is kind.

16:04.610 --> 16:07.100
He ordered the nightmare fields burned
and left an exit

16:07.100 --> 16:08.610
for us villagers to leave safely.

16:10.060 --> 16:12.130
Mr. Mu is truly extraordinary.

16:13.980 --> 16:15.890
May I ask, in these past days,

16:16.420 --> 16:18.130
have you seen anyone from the Six Sects?

16:18.340 --> 16:19.490
I did hear

16:20.180 --> 16:21.070
that there's

16:21.070 --> 16:22.180
Cai Pingshu's niece here.

16:22.700 --> 16:24.100
She plans to join hands with Mr. Mu

16:24.100 --> 16:25.220
to strike against Chief Nie.

16:27.300 --> 16:28.140
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

16:30.890 --> 16:33.490
Just find the Jade Sunflower quietly.

16:33.490 --> 16:35.650
Why get tangled up with Mr. Mu?

16:35.650 --> 16:36.650
No point in talking more.

16:36.650 --> 16:37.940
Let's go in and see for ourselves.

16:38.220 --> 16:39.060
Lord Song.

16:42.940 --> 16:44.370
You... know me?

16:44.610 --> 16:45.450
I don't.

16:45.850 --> 16:47.100
Someone told me,

16:47.100 --> 16:49.770
if a man is well-dressed, imposing,

16:49.920 --> 16:50.890
and has a slight belly,

16:51.340 --> 16:52.980
it must be Lord Song.

16:53.650 --> 16:54.490
Did this person

16:54.650 --> 16:56.610
have a message for us?

16:56.850 --> 16:58.220
You must be Lord Qi.

16:58.220 --> 16:59.420
Yes.

16:59.420 --> 17:01.010
Then I'll deliver the message.

17:02.180 --> 17:03.770
"Master, forgive me."

17:03.770 --> 17:05.570
"I've disappointed you again."

17:05.570 --> 17:07.220
"Once I return,
I won't run off anymore."

17:08.290 --> 17:09.130
This girl...

17:10.010 --> 17:10.860
"Lord Song."

17:10.860 --> 17:12.570
"What Yuzhi is looking for
is right here."

17:12.570 --> 17:13.810
"You'd better not go in."

17:13.810 --> 17:16.220
"Or complications
might make us lose it."

17:17.620 --> 17:18.620
Alright.

17:19.220 --> 17:20.060
Message delivered.

17:20.330 --> 17:21.220
You two,

17:21.220 --> 17:22.070
I'll take my leave.

17:22.420 --> 17:23.290
Thank you.

17:26.920 --> 17:29.660
How did these two kids get involved in
the demon sect's civil strife?

17:30.050 --> 17:31.810
There's no hiding it anymore.

17:32.090 --> 17:33.330
We both ordered

17:33.330 --> 17:34.660
Zhao and Yuzhi

17:34.660 --> 17:36.290
to the demon sect for intelligence.

17:36.290 --> 17:37.130
But

17:37.580 --> 17:38.980
they were discovered by the demon sect.

17:39.530 --> 17:40.770
That's how the rumors started.

17:41.980 --> 17:42.940
Yunke,

17:42.940 --> 17:45.940
I always thought
you were slow and rigid.

17:45.940 --> 17:48.140
Never knew you were
so clever and flexible.

17:59.730 --> 18:02.090
Xiong Qianjin treated
that woman with great respect.

18:02.090 --> 18:04.770
So I guessed she holds
a high position in the Li Sect.

18:04.770 --> 18:06.420
Too bad we're one step too late.

18:06.900 --> 18:08.180
What did Xiong Qianjin call her?

18:08.620 --> 18:09.770
He called her Lady Sun.

18:15.220 --> 18:16.420
Look at these roots.

18:16.420 --> 18:18.980
They're the same as the herbs
Lady Sun had.

18:21.980 --> 18:22.940
It's poison smoke.

18:23.430 --> 18:24.770
Destroying the herbs isn't enough.

18:24.770 --> 18:26.290
They also laid such a vicious trap.

18:26.570 --> 18:28.180
Such an elaborate setup.

18:28.420 --> 18:29.900
Seems we're on the right track.

18:32.660 --> 18:33.940
Black roots, short hairs.

18:33.940 --> 18:35.050
I've never seen a plant like this

18:35.050 --> 18:36.700
in the Compendium of Herbs.

18:36.700 --> 18:37.860
It's the Beichen Orchid.

18:37.860 --> 18:39.860
This herb really can
prolong life and detoxify.

18:39.860 --> 18:41.620
Zhao, I'll take you somewhere.

18:42.530 --> 18:43.370
Oh right.

18:43.370 --> 18:44.900
This is the Li Sect's forbidden ground.

18:45.530 --> 18:46.900
No outsiders are allowed in.

18:46.900 --> 18:47.840
Then I...

18:47.840 --> 18:48.760
You're not an outsider.

18:48.900 --> 18:49.740
Let's go.

18:54.100 --> 18:57.380
(Carefree)

19:00.730 --> 19:01.860
This is Carefree.

19:02.940 --> 19:05.180
Every brick and tile,
every blade of grass and tree.

19:05.860 --> 19:08.010
All were personally overseen
by my father.

19:08.770 --> 19:10.140
Your father had fine taste.

19:13.180 --> 19:14.530
After he passed away,

19:14.860 --> 19:16.660
Uncle Cheng
took over the management here.

19:17.660 --> 19:18.810
That is the Beichen Orchid.

19:20.290 --> 19:21.290
This flower

19:21.290 --> 19:22.660
looks like the Withered Branch.

19:22.660 --> 19:23.980
It was my father's cherished treasure.

19:25.660 --> 19:27.050
Said to be rare in the world.

19:27.050 --> 19:28.940
My father tried many ways.

19:28.940 --> 19:30.330
Only obtained this single plant.

19:35.330 --> 19:36.180
Let's give it a try.

19:38.300 --> 19:40.030
♪In days gone by♪

19:40.340 --> 19:41.890
♪Willows swayed gently♪

19:42.190 --> 19:44.940
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

19:45.910 --> 19:47.100
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

19:47.110 --> 19:48.580
♪A fleeting glance♪

19:48.750 --> 19:49.660
♪And then♪

19:49.670 --> 19:52.620
♪Love consumed me♪

19:53.430 --> 19:54.980
♪Now I think of you♪

19:55.380 --> 19:57.020
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

19:57.280 --> 19:58.620
♪Alas, we parted♪

19:58.980 --> 19:59.820
Uncle Cheng.

20:00.950 --> 20:01.900
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

20:02.530 --> 20:03.370
Mr. Mu.

20:03.390 --> 20:04.420
♪Scattered petals♪

20:04.430 --> 20:06.660
♪Cover the ground♪

20:07.720 --> 20:09.980
♪Such should be our meeting♪

20:11.940 --> 20:12.780
Zhao.

20:14.860 --> 20:17.580
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

20:17.680 --> 20:21.670
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

20:22.330 --> 20:25.030
♪Such should be our meeting♪

20:25.210 --> 20:28.720
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

20:28.730 --> 20:29.730
It really works.

20:29.870 --> 20:32.440
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

20:34.220 --> 20:35.060
Uncle Cheng.

20:35.420 --> 20:37.250
Take the remaining herbs to Guanyue.

20:37.250 --> 20:38.330
Use them to cure Xing

20:38.330 --> 20:39.940
and the sect members'
corpse slave poison.

20:40.380 --> 20:41.420
I'll leave at once.

20:42.490 --> 20:43.330
Uncle Cheng.

20:45.140 --> 20:45.980
Thank you.

20:50.730 --> 20:51.570
Zhao.

20:51.770 --> 20:52.620
What are you up to?

20:52.620 --> 20:53.980
Beichen Orchid is so effective.

20:54.530 --> 20:56.900
Why not try it to
cleanse your poison too?

20:57.290 --> 20:58.250
No need.

20:58.250 --> 20:59.330
What's the harm in a try?

21:03.570 --> 21:04.660
You just recovered.

21:05.340 --> 21:06.770
Don't recklessly use your inner power.

21:11.330 --> 21:13.010
If you really care about me,

21:13.620 --> 21:15.140
after I die from the poison,

21:15.940 --> 21:17.700
ask them for a handful of my ashes

21:17.700 --> 21:18.540
to carry with you.

21:19.940 --> 21:21.220
Who wants to carry your ashes?

21:23.140 --> 21:24.660
Will you forget me, Zhao?

21:25.330 --> 21:27.490
When you have children
and grandchildren,

21:27.900 --> 21:29.250
grow old and gray,

21:29.700 --> 21:31.700
will you never mention me to them?

21:32.090 --> 21:32.930
Me?

21:35.620 --> 21:36.900
Children and grandchildren?

21:55.730 --> 21:56.940
The moon

21:57.980 --> 21:58.820
is so bright tonight.

22:10.010 --> 22:11.250
I often miss

22:12.180 --> 22:13.290
the days we lived together

22:13.860 --> 22:15.090
at Qingque Sect.

22:20.700 --> 22:21.540
Zhao.

22:22.180 --> 22:23.570
Those were my happiest,

22:25.420 --> 22:26.900
and most peaceful days.

22:48.810 --> 22:50.490
This wrist guard is so unique.

22:52.900 --> 22:54.010
Is it yours?

22:54.530 --> 22:55.860
It's a memento from my father.

22:59.220 --> 23:00.290
Since I was little,

23:00.290 --> 23:01.420
I'd often see Father

23:01.420 --> 23:02.980
staring at those wrist guards,
lost in thought.

23:04.380 --> 23:05.220
I think

23:05.700 --> 23:07.250
they must have an extraordinary origin.

23:08.090 --> 23:09.860
That's why Father
treasures them so much.

23:17.380 --> 23:18.220
Zhao,

23:19.810 --> 23:20.770
lie with me for a while.

23:21.730 --> 23:22.660
I'm tired.

23:27.290 --> 23:28.290
What are you up to now?

23:39.220 --> 23:40.570
During my time at the Li Sect,

23:43.330 --> 23:45.010
I've been surrounded by enemies,

23:45.860 --> 23:47.180
worn out from constant worry.

23:49.490 --> 23:50.980
Only when you're by my side

23:52.660 --> 23:54.180
do I feel a little peace.

24:07.090 --> 24:10.300
(Qinglong Altar)
Thank you. Thank you.

24:10.300 --> 24:13.420
Thank you. Thank you.

24:17.090 --> 24:18.860
Zhao didn't return all night yesterday.

24:18.860 --> 24:20.050
Has your gu poison been cured?

24:20.660 --> 24:22.700
How do you know she was gone all night?

24:23.330 --> 24:25.250
Were you waiting outside all night?

24:25.620 --> 24:27.090
I came here with Zhao.

24:27.090 --> 24:28.860
I should keep an eye on her safety.

24:28.860 --> 24:30.220
Do you have a problem with that, Mr. Mu?

24:32.140 --> 24:32.980
Zhao.

24:34.330 --> 24:36.860
There are still a few villagers
who need qi healing.

24:36.860 --> 24:38.090
Can you help them?

24:38.420 --> 24:39.380
I'll go right away.

24:41.940 --> 24:42.780
I'll help you.

24:43.290 --> 24:44.220
Mr. Mu.

24:46.180 --> 24:47.420
May I speak with you privately?

24:49.530 --> 24:51.250
You were the one who

24:51.250 --> 24:52.140
snuck into Carefree, right?

24:54.090 --> 24:55.290
When I was nine,

24:56.330 --> 24:58.180
my mother knew her days were numbered.

24:58.860 --> 25:00.530
She told me many things.

25:00.530 --> 25:01.570
I've heard your mother,

25:01.570 --> 25:02.810
Lady Qinglian,

25:02.810 --> 25:03.980
was extremely wise and resourceful.

25:03.980 --> 25:05.380
May I ask

25:05.380 --> 25:06.770
what advice did she give you

25:06.770 --> 25:07.810
before she passed?

25:08.220 --> 25:09.290
Everything in the world

25:10.050 --> 25:11.490
bows to one word,

25:12.660 --> 25:13.500
"Momentum."

25:14.860 --> 25:16.140
Go with the momentum,

25:16.140 --> 25:17.330
achieve double the result.

25:18.140 --> 25:19.180
Go against it,

25:19.860 --> 25:22.530
and even someone
as mighty as Nie Hengcheng

25:22.980 --> 25:25.220
will end up in ruin.

25:25.660 --> 25:26.770
Then tell me, Song,

25:28.010 --> 25:29.010
what is momentum?

25:30.330 --> 25:31.420
On a cosmic scale,

25:31.940 --> 25:34.700
the sun rises and sets. Rivers flow east.
Mountains stand in silence.

25:35.570 --> 25:37.050
No matter your toil,

25:37.050 --> 25:38.700
the sun still falls as it should.

25:39.020 --> 25:40.380
Even with the blood of a crying cuckoo,

25:40.380 --> 25:41.980
the moon will still return on time.

25:41.980 --> 25:43.140
On a human scale,

25:43.730 --> 25:45.250
it is the fate of a nation or a sect.

25:45.250 --> 25:46.330
A person's path in life.

25:47.180 --> 25:48.020
Or

25:48.980 --> 25:50.940
the success or failure of a marriage.

25:50.940 --> 25:53.140
Just old clichés, really.

25:53.140 --> 25:54.770
I thought the same when I was young.

25:55.140 --> 25:56.940
But everything my mother predicted

25:57.380 --> 25:59.050
came true, without exception.

25:59.900 --> 26:01.330
Mr. Mu, you're extremely intelligent.

26:02.380 --> 26:03.250
Can't you see

26:03.250 --> 26:05.420
the momentum between you and Zhao now?

26:06.660 --> 26:08.660
You were born into the demonic sect,

26:08.660 --> 26:10.530
while she belongs to
the Six Sects of Beichen.

26:10.530 --> 26:12.010
She has loving parents,

26:12.010 --> 26:13.380
caring elders,

26:13.380 --> 26:14.530
and harmonious siblings.

26:15.860 --> 26:17.490
She has so much to cherish.

26:18.250 --> 26:19.770
So that's your point.

26:21.090 --> 26:24.050
I wondered why you had the time to

26:24.050 --> 26:25.570
chat with me about old memories.

26:25.570 --> 26:26.700
Rest assured, Mr. Mu.

26:27.860 --> 26:29.860
I won't say a word or do anything

26:29.860 --> 26:30.770
to interfere with Zhao.

26:31.220 --> 26:32.060
Back then,

26:32.810 --> 26:33.660
she refused to tell me

26:33.660 --> 26:35.810
the details of getting the saliva
from the Polar Snow Mountains.

26:35.810 --> 26:36.650
But I believe

26:37.140 --> 26:39.140
you helped a great deal, Mr. Mu.

26:39.770 --> 26:42.010
Zhao's feelings for you
are beyond doubt.

26:42.010 --> 26:43.420
Nothing others say will change that.

26:45.490 --> 26:47.250
But my mother also said that

26:47.660 --> 26:49.730
no matter how deep the affection,

26:50.330 --> 26:52.250
it can't stand against
the momentum of the world.

26:53.660 --> 26:55.730
Mr. Mu, why force it?

26:55.730 --> 26:56.570
What a coincidence.

26:58.290 --> 26:59.980
I just love forcing things.

27:03.090 --> 27:04.010
It's all done.

27:09.620 --> 27:11.180
What are you two talking about?

27:11.660 --> 27:12.660
So serious.

27:14.380 --> 27:15.250
Just idle chatter.

27:27.700 --> 27:28.540
I heard

27:28.700 --> 27:31.420
Mu Qingyan escaped
the poison smoke in the herb garden.

27:31.770 --> 27:34.010
And cured the corpse slave's gu poison.

27:39.730 --> 27:40.630
Dear,

27:40.630 --> 27:41.810
he's tricky,

27:41.910 --> 27:43.050
but if you need me,

27:43.050 --> 27:44.010
I'll obey your orders.

27:44.010 --> 27:45.050
Dad.

27:47.010 --> 27:47.850
Si'en,

27:49.840 --> 27:51.230
why haven't you done your lessons?

27:51.410 --> 27:52.410
Dad,

27:52.550 --> 27:55.960
I heard the Mu clan is coming to
cause trouble again.

27:56.200 --> 27:57.740
I'm worried about you.

27:59.360 --> 28:00.570
Ruxin,

28:00.780 --> 28:01.900
the child is still young.

28:01.900 --> 28:04.340
No need to tell him such things.

28:04.340 --> 28:06.180
Even if he hears it by chance,

28:06.180 --> 28:08.140
we should guide him properly.

28:08.160 --> 28:10.790
The strategist came to
teach Si'en martial arts today.

28:10.900 --> 28:13.060
Si'en asked why he was injured

28:13.060 --> 28:15.020
and found out naturally.

28:15.020 --> 28:16.060
Besides,

28:16.060 --> 28:18.060
it's common knowledge.

28:18.060 --> 28:19.660
Why hide it?

28:20.180 --> 28:21.900
Do you have any scruples, Sister?

28:22.380 --> 28:23.460
Ruxin,

28:24.020 --> 28:25.620
that's not what I meant.

28:28.820 --> 28:29.740
Dear.

28:30.390 --> 28:31.460
Dad.

28:32.020 --> 28:35.100
Is that Mu Qingyan truly that powerful?

28:36.020 --> 28:37.060
Him?

28:37.060 --> 28:38.780
He's just someone
who should've died long ago.

28:39.100 --> 28:40.780
A loser I defeated before.

28:41.180 --> 28:42.100
Si'en, come here.

28:42.740 --> 28:45.100
Take a look at this
Map of Mountains and Seas.

28:45.340 --> 28:46.380
(Demon Realm)
One day,

28:46.380 --> 28:47.540
all this will be yours.

28:47.860 --> 28:49.500
The Li Sect will belong to
Nie clan from now on.

28:50.300 --> 28:52.180
No longer tied to the Mu clan.

28:54.100 --> 28:55.180
Yes.

28:55.820 --> 28:56.980
Everything will be Si'en's.

28:57.100 --> 28:58.220
Don't touch me.

28:59.100 --> 29:00.140
Alright, Si'en.

29:00.140 --> 29:01.700
Time for you to
get back to your studies.

29:03.180 --> 29:04.220
You all head back first.

29:05.060 --> 29:06.220
I'll come see you tonight.

29:06.220 --> 29:07.060
No need.

29:07.450 --> 29:09.100
Si'en has been sleeping early
these days.

29:20.720 --> 29:22.260
Dear, you treat Ruxin
with such kindness.

29:22.780 --> 29:24.740
Too bad she's so stubborn.

29:24.740 --> 29:25.610
Dear.

29:25.610 --> 29:27.260
Don't be sad.

29:27.260 --> 29:28.220
Let her be.

29:28.620 --> 29:30.300
After all,
she's Uncle's adopted daughter.

29:30.900 --> 29:33.580
And the wife
Uncle personally chose for me.

29:34.360 --> 29:35.220
In truth,

29:35.220 --> 29:36.380
I've long wanted to

29:36.380 --> 29:37.820
make you my co-wife.

29:38.540 --> 29:39.500
But unfortunately,

29:40.060 --> 29:42.460
you can't let go of your son.

29:47.700 --> 29:49.780
Chief, I can never repay your kindness.

29:50.420 --> 29:51.860
I know my status is low.

29:51.860 --> 29:53.140
I don't dare hope for such things.

29:53.910 --> 29:54.900
But for the Chief,

29:54.900 --> 29:55.830
for the Li Sect,

29:55.840 --> 29:57.040
I'm willing to give up everything.

29:57.050 --> 29:57.890
Including...

30:12.700 --> 30:14.380
I know it's hard for you, Lady.

30:14.980 --> 30:15.820
But I have to

30:16.220 --> 30:17.940
ask this of you.

30:31.480 --> 30:32.820
The Bliss Palace is full of traps.

30:33.380 --> 30:34.660
The troops of the Demonic Camp are

30:34.820 --> 30:36.220
(Bliss Palace)
stationed at Yaoyue Pass.

30:36.320 --> 30:37.340
At dusk, during You hour,

30:37.740 --> 30:38.780
we'll set out at once.

30:38.940 --> 30:40.460
Reach the Yaoyue Pass by You hour,

30:40.660 --> 30:43.060
launch the attack at Xu hour.

30:43.060 --> 30:44.100
Count us in for the attack on

30:44.100 --> 30:44.940
Bliss Palace.

30:49.060 --> 30:49.900
Zhao.

30:51.060 --> 30:52.300
Let's step outside first.

30:52.300 --> 30:54.180
Let Miss Cai and the Mr. Mu
talk in peace.

31:10.820 --> 31:11.660
Zhao.

31:12.260 --> 31:13.100
A few months ago,

31:13.780 --> 31:14.980
the masked man who snuck into

31:14.980 --> 31:16.740
Qingque Sect and
kidnapped Chang Ning and me

31:16.740 --> 31:17.580
was you.

31:17.580 --> 31:18.980
You have sharp eyes, Miss.

31:18.980 --> 31:19.940
It was indeed me.

31:26.820 --> 31:28.300
You two were in cahoots all along!

31:30.980 --> 31:31.860
Not the first time.

31:33.020 --> 31:34.300
After the Chang Fort was destroyed,

31:34.700 --> 31:36.140
I was ordered by Nie Zhe to

31:36.140 --> 31:37.700
sneak into Qingque Sect
and catch Chang Ning.

31:38.140 --> 31:39.100
I never thought

31:39.580 --> 31:41.260
Chang Ning was
the long-lost Young Master.

31:42.220 --> 31:43.860
And I even risked my life to save you.

31:44.940 --> 31:46.620
Why aren't you acting in operas, Mr. Mu?

31:47.020 --> 31:47.860
Such a pity.

31:49.620 --> 31:51.140
Zhao loves watching plays so much,

31:51.380 --> 31:52.660
if I don't put on a good act,

31:53.060 --> 31:54.540
wouldn't that disappoint Zhao?

31:55.020 --> 31:57.420
To preserve his strength
and eliminate Nie Zhe,

31:57.420 --> 31:59.220
Mr. Mu endured humiliation
and bent when necessary.

31:59.220 --> 32:01.380
Staying in a place
like Qingque Sect for months.

32:01.380 --> 32:02.780
Truly, a model for us all.

32:03.380 --> 32:04.860
A place like Qingque Sect?

32:05.120 --> 32:06.020
Is it a terrible place?

32:06.260 --> 32:08.300
Besides the ten years
I spent with my father,

32:08.700 --> 32:09.940
the days at Qingque Sect

32:10.380 --> 32:11.340
were the happiest

32:12.260 --> 32:13.420
of my life.

32:16.420 --> 32:18.540
You always mention your father.

32:18.540 --> 32:20.340
Why never your mom?

32:22.020 --> 32:23.420
- Mr. Mu' mother...
- Everyone,

32:23.420 --> 32:25.540
Mr. Mu is still my child, after all.

32:25.540 --> 32:26.980
I can't stop worrying about him.

32:27.580 --> 32:28.900
Can you make an exception?

32:28.900 --> 32:30.300
Let me see him once.

32:30.300 --> 32:31.900
What the hell.

32:31.900 --> 32:33.420
Speak of the devil, and she appears.

32:42.580 --> 32:43.420
Qingyan.

32:45.580 --> 32:47.420
Since hearing you're back,

32:48.300 --> 32:49.900
my heart has been in turmoil.

32:49.900 --> 32:51.140
I've thought of you day and night.

32:51.140 --> 32:52.900
Only wish to see you once.

32:52.900 --> 32:54.300
Seeing you so thin

32:54.940 --> 32:56.900
truly breaks my heart.

32:56.900 --> 32:58.140
I've been back for two months.

32:58.460 --> 32:59.820
If you truly missed me,

33:00.420 --> 33:01.820
why didn't you come sooner?

33:02.140 --> 33:04.020
There are things beyond my control.

33:04.580 --> 33:05.780
Nie Zhe…

33:05.780 --> 33:07.340
He imprisoned me
within the Bliss Palace.

33:07.900 --> 33:08.940
He called it protection.

33:08.940 --> 33:10.300
But it was imprisonment and threats.

33:11.300 --> 33:13.020
I miss you every day.

33:13.020 --> 33:14.420
My heart wrenching in pain,

33:15.140 --> 33:16.940
yet I could do nothing.

33:17.740 --> 33:20.460
But I saw you going out to gather herbs.

33:22.780 --> 33:25.140
You were the one at the Youming Path.

33:27.260 --> 33:28.940
That was because
Nie Zhe forced me to go.

33:29.460 --> 33:30.380
If I refuse to go,

33:31.020 --> 33:32.700
he'd beat me brutally.

33:32.700 --> 33:34.020
These days,

33:34.020 --> 33:35.620
whenever he's upset,

33:35.620 --> 33:37.340
he takes it out on me.

33:40.420 --> 33:42.540
Though I live in hardship,

33:42.540 --> 33:45.460
my longing and love for you

33:45.460 --> 33:47.300
have never changed.

33:48.700 --> 33:49.900
Qingyan, I just hope you

33:49.900 --> 33:52.140
can understand your mother's hardships.

33:52.140 --> 33:54.100
Your acting

33:54.100 --> 33:55.220
still lacks some conviction.

33:56.140 --> 33:57.580
If you truly want it to be convincing,

33:58.820 --> 34:01.220
those wounds should look deeper.

34:01.780 --> 34:03.100
More realistic that way.

34:03.540 --> 34:04.420
Qingyan,

34:05.380 --> 34:06.980
how can you speak to me like that?

34:08.380 --> 34:10.140
I may have made mistakes in the past,

34:10.620 --> 34:11.940
but my love for my son

34:11.940 --> 34:13.420
is as clear as heaven and earth!

34:13.420 --> 34:15.230
Spare me the "motherly love
and filial piety" nonsense!

34:19.580 --> 34:21.260
We both know

34:21.620 --> 34:22.780
what kind of people we are.

34:24.300 --> 34:25.460
I tolerate you,

34:26.500 --> 34:27.700
and I've let you stay this long.

34:28.100 --> 34:29.780
Not because you gave birth to me,

34:30.700 --> 34:32.700
but because I promised my father.

34:33.660 --> 34:35.780
If you keep pushing your limits,

34:36.940 --> 34:38.220
don't blame me

34:39.220 --> 34:40.580
for being disrespectful.

34:45.020 --> 34:45.860
Qingyan.

34:52.460 --> 34:53.300
Qingyan.

34:53.540 --> 34:54.700
This is your Fuying Sword.

34:54.700 --> 34:56.540
You left it at
the Bliss Palace back then.

34:56.540 --> 34:57.860
It belonged to your late father.

34:58.620 --> 34:59.860
You must have missed it dearly.

35:00.420 --> 35:02.380
I risked my life today to retrieve it.

35:03.380 --> 35:04.220
Qingyan.

35:05.140 --> 35:06.620
Will you trust me now?

35:12.860 --> 35:13.700
Guanyue.

35:13.700 --> 35:14.540
Yes.

35:14.540 --> 35:15.940
Arrange a place for Madam to stay.

35:16.220 --> 35:17.060
Madam.

35:17.420 --> 35:18.260
Please come with me.

35:28.740 --> 35:29.780
Your mother, she...

35:29.780 --> 35:30.740
She's not my mother.

36:02.820 --> 36:03.660
Dad.

36:12.260 --> 36:13.100
The Dao's vessel

36:13.780 --> 36:15.260
is never full.

36:16.500 --> 36:18.580
This sword is named Fuying.
(*Fuying: Never full.)

36:19.260 --> 36:20.340
May my son

36:22.220 --> 36:23.820
live a long and peaceful life.

36:42.820 --> 36:43.700
Father.

37:02.680 --> 37:13.340
=Generation to Generation=

37:32.100 --> 37:36.510
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

37:37.075 --> 37:41.690
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

37:42.030 --> 37:46.595
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

37:47.120 --> 37:51.420
♪Free to wander in the world♪

37:54.365 --> 37:59.065
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:59.590 --> 38:03.880
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

38:04.540 --> 38:08.570
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

38:08.885 --> 38:14.010
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

38:14.585 --> 38:19.395
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:19.610 --> 38:23.780
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:24.505 --> 38:28.440
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:28.940 --> 38:34.215
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

38:56.945 --> 39:02.075
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:02.440 --> 39:06.810
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:07.075 --> 39:11.205
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:11.390 --> 39:16.965
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
